{"tid":2386644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突 發）英 國 移 民 apps 登 陸 熱 門 排 行 榜 第 九 位","createTime":"2021-01-29T17:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T02:15:30.000Z","uid":361751,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"25a11a8af8b4d051592251041bbf0741667d5083","tid":2386644,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FaF2MDo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFaF2MDo.png&h=0c948f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家一齊下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收支那皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eb29f7fb50ca31a101929c658af212c6613374","tid":2386644,"uid":361751,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCFaVxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCFaVxB.png&h=34cc4729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒婆瞓未呀<br />\n<br />\n今次有咩回應<br />\n<br />\n下載率高過ig喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90cfc282df30ef24ec8693cb61c0e7130d6f4f","tid":2386644,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"f61145b68e7f7a4ab66fc005a4922a7ac0ec1444","tid":2386644,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"樓主精神分裂？"},{"pid":"a6a8f7f0040fa20dfb1773b89b151ecd15967597","tid":2386644,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f61145b68e7f7a4ab66fc005a4922a7ac0ec1444","tid":2386644,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"樓主精神分裂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"乜春？"},{"pid":"131dbf2182197f3bbfd266e93f5208ed43a1f683","tid":2386644,"uid":300690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"當二百萬人為無物嘅人 係唔會覺得有大量人移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba90074bfe96cda8c9d335c4489725781262f605","tid":2386644,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08017159e7876f94e28a488b991863cf5bc88f34","tid":2386644,"uid":92299,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy"